title: Did Mussollini Really Make the Trains Run on Time?
description: Fascism is loved by few, but many at least credit Mussolini's heavy-handed rule for making Italy's notoriously disastrous train system operate effectively. Was this actually true or more of Il Duce's propaganda?
itunes:author: Scott Rank, PhD
